title: Robin Hood (Eclipse)
description:
'Robin Hood' by Valerie Jones, Tim Truman and Christopher Schenck is the next entry in the Eclipse Comics Upload Project.

Robin Hood was a three-issue mini-series released in 1991 by Eclipse. It was written by Jones, penciled by Truman and finished in watercolors by Schenck. 

The story revolves around Robin Hood's return from the Crusades. It was very controversial at the time for its explicit depiction of Robin tea-bagging Friar Tuck, while the remaining Merry Men used them for bukkake targets.

Nah. I'm just yanking your chain. It's ROBIN HOOD, dude! You KNOW what it's about!
